propDescriptions.action: The action to display in the card header.
propDescriptions.avatar: The Avatar for the Card Header.
propDescriptions.classes: Sobrescreve ou extende os estilos aplicados para o componente. Veja a API CSS abaixo para maiores detalhes.
propDescriptions.component: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propDescriptions.disableTypography: If true, subheader and title won't be wrapped by a Typography component. This can be useful to render an alternative Typography variant by wrapping the title text, and optional subheader text with the Typography component.
propDescriptions.subheaderTypographyProps: These props will be forwarded to the subheader (as long as disableTypography is not true).
propDescriptions.sx: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles. See the `sx` page for more details.
propDescriptions.title: O conteúdo do componente.
propDescriptions.titleTypographyProps: These props will be forwarded to the title (as long as disableTypography is not true).
